      "writtenOn": "2021-06-03T08:50:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Since \"git rev-parse --show-toplevel\" might resolve symlinks, it\u0027s possible that currDir doesn\u0027t have gitRoot as a prefix. For example:\n \n [nya@yoru git]% ls -l\n total 4\n drwxr-xr-x 4 nya primarygroup 4096 Jun  3 08:47 a\n lrwxrwxrwx 1 nya primarygroup    1 Jun  3 08:47 b -\u003e a\n [nya@yoru git]% cd b/x\n [nya@yoru x]% git rev-parse --show-toplevel\n /usr/local/google/home/nya/tmp/git/a\n \nYou can call filepath.Abs to canonicalize file paths.\nhttps://pkg.go.dev/path/filepath#Abs",
